      },
      "date": "2015-05-29 20:21:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review-1\n\nI don't think there is sufficient explanation for why this is the best approach.  It seems worryingly complicated to me, and would appear to violate very basic architectural decisions that we have made in the Lustre recovery system.  Lets have a discussion in ticket LU-6657 about what the right way is to solve this problem.",
